				\usepackage{amssymb}
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$${\text{HRT = (}}V ) / (Q ),$$\end{document}where V is reactor volume and Q is influent flow rate
